esenting this case?<br>No\"\"</p>\n<p>Do you have any attorney for this case?<br>A. No</p>\n<p>Are you working with another Law firm?<br>A. No</p>\n<p>Do you have a smoking history?<br>A. No never&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Have you ever been diagnosed with Hepatitis B and C?<br>A. No (Never)</p>\n<p>Have you had any organ transplants?<br>A. No (Never)</p>\n<p>Did anyone try to coach you?<br>A. No</p>\n<p>Do you have your medical records?<br>A. Yes</p>\n<p>Can you submit your medical records?<br>A. Actually my medical records are in my storage. If you want I can get it but it would take 3-4 days to get them from my storage OR else you can also get them from the hospital.</p>\n<p>How do you know about this lawsuit?<br>A. I found this on social media and applied online.</p>\n<p>If we find something wrong with your case then we might charge you.<br>A. Yes, I have given all the valid information\"</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2025-08-19 20:15:29', '2025-08-19 20:14:07', '2025-08-19 20:14:07'),
