(203, 'updated', 'model', 'updated', 'updated', 'Modules\\Contacts\\Models\\Contact', 22, 'Modules\\Users\\Models\\User', 3, 'Amit', '{\"attributes\":{\"cf_comment\":{\"label\":\"Comment\",\"value\":\"cervical cancer, tumor. Breast tumor in Tumor in spine also\\n\\nName:- Dana Crictendon\\nNumber:- 3149439716\\nDOB:- 9\\/3\\/1983\\nEmail -  dana crictendon126@gmail.com\\nAddress:- 4330 Dar Ln St. Louis, MO 63123\\n\\n\\n\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"1.Did anyone in your family or you used Roundup, Paraquat, Hair Relaxer?\\n-I have used Roundup\\n\\nDid you face any major complications after using Roundup?\\nI was diagnosed with Non Hodgkin\'s Lymphoma Stage 1\\n\\n1. For which product are you filing for the lawsuit?\\nA. Roundup Pesticide (Brand name - Monsanto)\\n\\n2. Have you used AGENT ORANGE?\\nA. No\\n\\n\\nPRODUCT USAGE\\n-When did you Started using Roundup : 12\\/04\\/2006 (23 Age)\\n-When did you stop using Roundup: 08\\/12\\/2021 (37Age)\\n-For how long did you use Roundup: Almost 15 years\\n**What was the type of Roundup: It was a WEED KILLER..\\n\\n**Purpose of using the Roundup : For residential purpose\\n\\n**Why did you use the Roundup : I used Roundup to Kill the Unwanted Weed & Wild Grass in my home backyard garden..\\n\\n**How often you use the Roundup: 4 times a month..\\n\\n**How did you use the Product: Sprayer\\n\\n**Was it Concentrated or Mixed: Both Depends which product was available in the store.\\n\\n**What was the Colour of the Roundup Liquid: Amber\\n\\nWhat was the Size of the Roundup Bottle: 2 Gallons\\n\\nWhat Color is the Round Up Bottle\\nGreen Bottle with a red cap\\n  \\n\\n--Where did you usually purchase Roundup from: The Home Depot\\n(7481 S Lindbergh Blvd, St. Louis, MO 63125)\\n\\n**Are you still using Roundup: NO..\\n\\n--Which address did you use Roundup:\\n4330 Dar LnSt. Louis, MO 63123\\n\\n**Why did you stop using Roundup: My doctor suggested not to use it anymore.as i was getting Side Effect\\n\\nCOMPLICATIONS\\n**Side Effects \\/ Complications: Loss of appetite, Night sweats, shortness of breath and Abdomen Pain.\\n\\n*How do you know the cancer was because of Roundup: Doctors were able to find TRACES of Roundup in the Biopsy Report..\\n\\nTEST\\n**What Tests did you go through:  Blood test, Urine test, CT Scan and Biopsy\\n\\n*A)Blood Test: They took my blood samples for the test.\\n\\n*B)CAT SCAN: They put Me in a tunnel like machine and scanned my whole body..\\n\\n*C)BIOPSY: Doctor inserted a needle on the upper left side of my abdomen and took so sample tissue from my spleen\\n\\n--When was the Test done:  08\\/12\\/2021\\n\\n**What was the result of the Tests: It Came POSITIVE Non-Hodgkin\'s Lymphoma\\n\\n--When were you diagnosed with Non-Hodgkins Lymphoma:  08\\/23\\/2021 (Age 37) \\n\\n--What was your age when diagnosed with Non-Hodgkin\\u2019s Lymphoma: 37 years old\\n\\n-What was the type of Lymphoma: B Cell Lymphoma\\n\\n*Which part of your body was affected: Spleen\\n\\nTREATMENT\\n**What treatments did you receive:  Spleen Surgery(08\\/25\\/2020), Injected Chemotherapy (6 Cycles For 6 Months), & Antibiotics (Amoxycillin)\\n\\n\\n*D)Spleen Surgery: they maid a cut on the upper left side of my Abdomen and Remove the spleen completely\\n\\n\\n\\n** Remission Period: For 3 Years but in 2023 my doctor informed that i am cancer free and i stopped my future treatments\\n\\nWhat was done in the Remission Period?\\n(Every 6 months I had to visit a hospital for Blood test and a CAT Scan to check if I am cancer free or not.\\n\\n--Cancer Free Date: I am cancer free (Oct\\/20\\/2023)\\n\\nDOCTOR, HOSPITAL & PHARMACY DETAILS\\n\\n--Doctor\\u2019s Name and Designation: Dr. Jacquelyn\\u202fL.\\u202fCarter ( Hematology )(314)\\u202f251\\u20116986\\n\\n--Hospital Name :  Mercy Hospital South\\n--hospital address- 10010 Kennerly Road, Sappington, MO 63128\\nHospital Phone Number: (314)\\u202f525\\u20111000\\n\\n--Pharmacy for Medicines: Walgreens Pharmacy\\n--Pharmacy Address: 1 Grasso Plaza, Affton, MO 63123\\n\\n32. Have you ever taken an HIV or AIDS test?\\nA. Yes. (Results came back negative)\\n\\n33. Do you have any attorney for this case?\\nA. No\\n\\n34. Are you working with another Law firm?\\nA. No\\n\\n35. Do you have a smoking history?\\nA. No never\\n\\n36. Have you ever been diagnosed with Hepatitis B and C?\\nA. No (Never)\\n\\n37. Have you had any organ transplants?\\nA. No (Never)\\n\\n38. Did anyone try to coach you?\\nA. No\\n\\n39. Do you have your medical records?\\nA. Yes\\n\\n40. Can you submit your medical records?\\nA. Actually my medical records are in my storage. If you want I can get it but it would take 3-4 days to get them from my storage OR else you can also get them from the\\u00a0hospital.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\\"\\\"\\\"\\\"\"}},\"old\":{\"cf_comment\":{\"label\":\"Comment\",\"value\":\"cervical cancer, tumor. Breast tumor in Tumor in spine also\"}}}', NULL, '2025-08-08 20:47:52', '2025-08-08 20:47:52'),
