(418, 'updated', 'model', 'updated', 'updated', 'Modules\\Contacts\\Models\\Contact', 49, 'Modules\\Users\\Models\\User', 3, 'Amit', '{\"attributes\":{\"cf_comment\":{\"label\":\"Comment\",\"value\":\"GENERATED FOR ROUNDUP\\n\\nName:- Virginia Cortez\\t\\nPhone Number:- 6198023637\\nEmail:- cortezginnie@gmail.com\\t\\nAddress:- 1311 Sunny Acres Ave Alpine CA 91901\\t\\nDOB:- 3\\/2\\/1963\\n\\n\\nDid anyone in your family or you used Roundup, Paraquat, Hair Relaxer?\\nAns - I have used Roundup\\n\\nDid you face any major complications after using Roundup?\\nAns - I was diagnosed with (NHL) Non Hodgkin\'s Lymphoma (Stage 1)(Pronunciation - NON HOTCH KINS LIM FOMAA)\\n\\n1. For which product are you filing for the lawsuit?\\nAns- Roundup\\n\\nWhat is the Brand name of Roundup?\\nAns- Monsanto\\n\\n2. Have you used AGENT ORANGE?\\nAns- No\\n\\n3. Where did you use the roundup?\\nAns- At residential area  (I used in my yard for weed killing and grass killing)\\n\\n4. How long were you using it?\\nA. 11 years.\\n\\n5. When did you start using it?\\nA. March 11th 2011 (Age: 48)\\n\\n6. When did you stop using it?\\nA. August 19th 2022 (Age: 59)\\n\\n7. Why did you stop using roundup?\\nA. As I started facing some side effects, the doctor told me to stop using it.\\n\\n8. What side effects were you facing after using roundup?\\nA. Night sweats, Breathing Problem, Swelling of my lymph nodes under my left armpit, Fatigue & Weight loss\\n\\n9. Did you consult any doctor for your side effects?\\nA. Yes, They ran some test on me which were Blood test, Urine test, MRI, CT scan, & Biopsy\\n\\nQ. When was the test Done?\\nA. August 19th 2022\\n\\nQ. What was the result of the test?\\nA. Biopsy was positive for Non-Hodgkin\'s Lymphoma (Stage 1)\\n\\nQ. How was the Biopsy performed?\\nA. They took some samples of tissue from the skin (Left side of my Armpit) and tested it.\\n\\n10. What was the complication?\\nA. Non-Hodgkin\'s Lymphoma (Pronunciation - NON HOTCH KINS LIM FOMAA) (Stage 1)\\n\\n11. Which body part was affected by cancer?\\nA. My Lymph Nodes (under my left Armpit).\\n\\n12. What type of lymphoma were you diagnosed with?\\nA. B-Cell Lymphoma\\n\\n13. What was the date when you were diagnosed with cancer?\\nA. August 26th 2022 (Age: 59)\\n\\n14. In which hospital were you diagnosed with cancer?\\nA. The Oncology Institute \\u2013 Hillcrest Clinic\\n\\n (3965 5th Ave., Suite 230, San Diego, CA 92103) ( (619) 605-0806)\\n\\n15. Name of the doctor who diagnosed you with cancer?\\nA. Dr. Jeffrey Andrey,- (619) 605-0806\\n(Doctor Designation - Hematologist)\\n\\n16. What was the hospitalization?\\nA. I was 7 days in the hospital and outpatient for 6 months\\n\\n17. What was the date when the doctor started your treatment?\\nA. They started my treatments from Sep 01th, 2022\\n\\n18. What were the treatments given to you when you were hospitalized?\\nA. Lymph nodes Surgery (Sep 01th, 2022), Injected Chemotherapy - 6 cycles for 6 months, (Chemo was injected through an IV), & Pain Medication (Bleomycin).\\n\\nHow was the Lymph node Surgery Done?\\nThey made a small cut under my left armpit and removed the infected Lymph nodes.\\n\\n19. Do you have any primary care physicians?\\nA.  No\\n\\n20. Are you cancer free?\\nA. Yes, November 06th 2024\\n\\n21. How long were you in the remission period?\\nA. For 3 Years but in 2024 my doctor informed me that I am cancer free and I stopped my further treatments.\\n\\n22. What is Remission?\\nA. It was a checkup session where doctors used to call me after every 6 months to do Blood tests and Ct Scan to check ups and see if I am cancer free or not.\\n\\n23. What type of roundup you were using?\\nA. Weed and Grass killer\\n\\n24. What was the size of the bottle?\\nA. 2 gallons.\\n\\n25. How often is it used?\\nA. Once a week.\\n\\n26. How did you apply it?\\nA. I was spraying it using a spray bottle.\\n\\n27. Was it concentrated or mixed?\\nA. Both\\n\\n28. What was the color of the roundup bottle?\\nA. It was a green color bottle with a red cap\\n\\n29. Color of the Roundup pesticide?\\nA. Amber\\n\\n30. From where did you purchase it?\\nA. Ace Hardware\\n(1347 Tavern Rd Ste C 4\\/5, Alpine, CA 91901)\\n\\n31. Pharmacy for buying medication\\nA. CVS Pharmacy\\n( 1385 Tavern Rd, Alpine, CA 91901)\\n\\n\\n32. Have you ever taken an HIV or AIDS test?\\nA. Yes. (Results came back negative)\\n\\n33. Do you have any attorney for this case?\\nA. No\\n\\n34. Are you working with another Law firm?\\nA. No\\n\\n35. Do you have a smoking history?\\nA. No never\\n\\n36. Have you ever been diagnosed with Hepatitis B and C?\\nA. No (Never)\\n\\n37. Have you had any organ transplants?\\nA. No (Never)\\n\\n38. Did anyone try to coach you?\\nA. No\\n\\n39. Do you have your medical records?\\nA. Yes\\n\\n40. Can you submit your medical records?\\nA. Actually my medical records are in my storage. If you want I can get it but it would take 3-4 days to get them from my storage OR else you can also get them from the hospital.\\n\\n41. How do you know about this lawsuit?\\nA. I found this on social media and applied online.\\n\\n42. If we find something wrong with your case then we might put you behind the bars\\nA. Yes, I have given all the valid information\"}},\"old\":{\"cf_comment\":{\"label\":\"Comment\",\"value\":\"GENERATED FOR ROUNDUP\"}}}', NULL, '2025-08-29 16:13:57', '2025-08-29 16:13:57'),
