(618, 'created', 'model', 'created', 'created', 'Modules\\Contacts\\Models\\Contact', 91, 'Modules\\Users\\Models\\User', 4, 'Akshay', '{\"attributes\":{\"user.name\":\"Akshay\",\"country.name\":null,\"source.name\":null,\"id\":91,\"email\":\"jrraymontoya@gmail.com\",\"uuid\":\"1ccd85b7-95a5-43f4-8494-13acd4c3f575\",\"user_id\":4,\"source_id\":null,\"first_name\":\"Arta\",\"last_name\":\"Montoya\",\"job_title\":null,\"avatar\":null,\"street\":\"19132 E 55th Pl\",\"city\":\"Denver\",\"state\":\"CO\",\"postal_code\":\"80249\",\"country_id\":null,\"import_id\":null,\"next_activity_date\":null,\"last_contacted_at\":null,\"cf_address\":{\"label\":\"Address\",\"value\":null},\"cf_comment\":{\"label\":\"Comment\",\"value\":\"Name:- Arta Montoya\\nPhone:- 3039154054\\nAddress:- 19132 E 55th Pl Denver CO 80249\\nEmail:- jrraymontoya@gmail.com    \\nDOB:- 8\\/7\\/1974 (51)\\n\\n1.Did anyone in your family or you used Roundup, Paraquat, Hair Relaxer, Johnson and Johnson OR AFFF?\\n-I have Used Johnson and Johnson\\n\\nDid you face any major complications after using Johnson and Johnson ?\\n- I was diagnosed with Ovarian Cancer\\n\\nHow Often Do You Use this Johnson and Johnson Baby Powder?\\n- Twice a day\\n\\nWhen was the first time you Started Using It?\\n- Since Teenager  (13 years old)\\n\\nAre you Still Using Johnson and Johnson Baby Powder or You Have Stopped Using It?\\n- I have stopped Using It \\n\\nWhen Did You Stop Using It?\\n- Aug 2018\\n\\nIn total, how many years have you used this product?\\nMore than 30 years\\n\\nWhy did you stop using it?\\n- I was facing Side effects so my Doctor Advised me to Stop Using it.\\n\\nWhat Side Effect were you Facing?\\n- Dry Skin, Abdominal Pain & Rashes\\n\\nWhen Did you Start Facing Side Effects?\\nFew Months before then I was Diagnosed with cancer\\n\\nDid you consult any Doctor after getting this Side Effect?\\nYes I consulted with an OBGYN Doctor in the Hospital.\\n\\nWhat did The Doctor Do?\\nAs I Know Doctor advice informed me to do some test which were\\nBlood Test, Urine Test & Biopsy\\n\\nWhat was the Result of the Test?\\nBIOPSY Test came back positive for OVARIAN CANCER STAGE 1\\n\\nWhen was the TEST done?\\nAug 13th 2018\\n\\nHow was the BIOPSY test Done?\\nIt was a Needle Biopsy, it was done with the help of Ultrasound they inserted a needle from my uterus and took some sample tissues from both of my ovaries\' and tested it \\n\\nWhat was the Major Complication?\\nOvarian Cancer Stage 1\\n\\nWhat Sub type of Ovarian Cancer were you diagnosed with?\\nEpithelial (EPI-THE-LIAL)\\n\\nWhen were you DIAGNOSED with ovarian cancer?\\nAug 17th 2018\\n\\nWhich Hospital were you taking your Treatment?\\nUCHealth University of Colorado Hospital\\n\\nHospital Address?\\n12605 E 16th Ave, Aurora, CO 80045\\n\\nHospital Phone Number?\\n-720-848-0000\\n\\nWhat TREATMENT did you receive in this hospital?\\nPartial Hysterectomy Surgery, Oral Chemotherapy (4 Cycles for 4 Months) & Pain Medications (Hydromorphone)\\n\\nWhat was Done in the Surgery?\\nThey removed Left Ovary.\\n\\nWhen was the Surgery Done?\\nAug 21th 2018\\n\\nName of the Doctor Who Diagnosed?\\n- Dr. Jaime Arruda (OBGYN)\\n\\nDoctor Phone Number?\\n(251)\\u202f433\\u20118838\\n\\nFor How Many Days Were You Hospitalized?\\n6 Days \\n\\nName of the Doctor Who did the treatment?\\nDr. Regina Brown (Oncologist)\\n\\nWhen were you discharged from the Hospital?\\n- Aug 27th 2018\\n\\nWhat was the Result Of BRCA Test?\\nNegative\\n\\nHIV\\/AIDS Test?\\nNegative\\n\\nFrom which Pharmacy you use to Purchase this Johnson and Johnson Baby Powder?\\nWalgreens Pharmacy\\n(6200 E Colfax Ave, Denver, CO 80220)\\n\\nAre you Cancer free?\\nYes (July 9th 2021)\\n\\nHistory of Endometriosis:- No\\n\\nHave you undergone Tubal Ligation:- No\\n\\nFamily History of Ovarian Cancer ? - No\\n\\nHave you suffered from infertility? - No\\n\\nDo you have any attorney for this case? -No\\n\\nAre you working with another Law firm? -No\\n\\nDo you have a smoking history?\\nNo never\\n\\nDo you have any Criminal History?\\nNo\\n\\nHave you ever been diagnosed with Hepatitis B and C?\\nNo (Never)\\n\\nHave you had any organ transplants?\\nNo (Never)\\n\\nDid anyone try to coach you?\\n No\\n\\nDo you have your medical records?\\nYes\\n\\nCan you submit your medical records?\\nA. Actually my medical records are in my storage. If you want I can get it but it would take 3-4 days to get them from my storage OR else you can also get them from the hospital.\"},\"cf_dob\":{\"label\":\"DOB\",\"value\":\"1974-08-07T00:00:00.000000Z\"}}}', NULL, '2025-09-12 16:40:26', '2025-09-12 16:40:26'),
